---
title: Creamy Pesto Grilling Cheese Ciabattas with Tomato, Balsamic Glaze & Potato Wedges
description: Our grilling cheese makes the perfect vegetarian sandwich, if we do say so ourselves. Before it’s cooked, the cheese starts off dense and firm. Sear that big hunk of cheese in a bit of oil, however, and the outside gets beautifully charred while the inside gets warm and soft. It took us by surprise, but by golly, it’s tasty. Layer that between toasty ciabatta buns along with juicy tomato, creamy pesto, and a rich balsamic glaze, and you have a next-level sandwich. Being cheesy never tasted so good.
